Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:35.06,Utama,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Kakiku bisa menyentuh dasar kolam manapun,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:37.12,Utama,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,dan lebih aman kalau berdua.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:45.13,Utama,Shiori,0,0,0,,Aku akan coba sedikit.
