Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:09.21,Utama,Shiori,0,0,0,,Enggak ada ya sudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.61,Utama,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Se-Senior?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:27.05,Utama,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Senior Mungil di Kantorku.{\i0}
